{"tid":1394574,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[講定先]若解放軍入黎係為咗清洗警隊，係引虎驅狼之計","createTime":"2019-08-01T12:49:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T10:41:26.000Z","uid":108757,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8fc2de6bb7b553f2957aae0aa02e46c6b8c294bb","tid":1394574,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T12:49:11.000Z","msg":"有人話出動解放軍係為咗收拾警隊，就算係咁，警隊收皮後，我地都唔可以讚頌解放軍，因為<span style=\"color: red;\">解放軍同警隊無一個係無辜的</span>！到時肯定有班傻仔出黎歌頌解放軍。<br />\n<br />\n解放軍係虎，警察係狼，引虎驅狼最終必然係<span style=\"color: red;\">虎患大於狼害</span>。我地必定要繼續反抗解放軍，外國勢力先有藉口相救！<br />\n<br />\n東漢末年，何進召董卓入京殺宦官，結果宦官係死晒，但係董卓之禍更甚於宦官！"},{"pid":"f75fb3f7f9fb99c7e6b6ebe4b518c64c7f51d79e","tid":1394574,"uid":8441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T12:50:51.000Z","msg":"中共想派兵焦土就一齊焦到底 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f966a2419bf4b41ebc83b66c8cd92297249fd579","tid":1394574,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T12:52:27.000Z","msg":"宋聯蒙滅金之後。。。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f78b1c86d17e571106ec2269456e714f5d4eb363","tid":1394574,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T12:52:29.000Z","msg":"唔想估中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8de28677b5ed29869957173afd159d03f930131f","tid":1394574,"uid":77905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T12:56:55.000Z","msg":"邊個戇鳩仔咁諗可以去打靶"},{"pid":"17d80ba69e2abef38a41855e43589d56272ff040","tid":1394574,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:01:37.000Z","msg":"天水圍讚警一事顯示，實有傻仔"},{"pid":"226e919d902eef02e6fbaafa923424e7b7fa2fb6","tid":1394574,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:12:55.000Z","msg":"又要推返上嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b37dbfbcef4ea9c5261480a11